commit.message:
re PR bootstrap/35216 (Out of memory building java)

PR bootstrap/35216
* scripts/makemake.tcl: Replace org/omg build with build of all its subpackages.
* sources.am: Regenerate.
* Makefile.in: Regenerate.

From-SVN: r133842
